---
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="border-t border-gray-90/30 bg-white dark:border-gray-10/50 dark:bg-gray-0">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8">
		<div class="xl:grid xl:grid-cols-3 xl:gap-12">
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<a href="/" class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter">
					<span class="gem-gradient-text">{SITE_TITLE}</span>
				</a>
				<p class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-50 dark:text-gray-90">
					숨겨진 보석 같은 사진 스팟을 찾는 여정.<br/>
					Gemmap과 함께 당신만의 특별한 장소를 기록하세요.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 xl:col-span-2 xl:mt-0">
				<div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-1 md:gap-8">
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-sm font-bold leading-6 text-gray-0 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Our Services</h3>
						<div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
							<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
								<div class="h-12 w-40 rounded-xl bg-gray-90 dark:bg-gray-10 animate-pulse flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-gray-50 font-bold border border-gray-90 dark:border-gray-10">Google Play</div>
								<div class="h-12 w-40 rounded-xl bg-gray-90 dark:bg-gray-10 animate-pulse flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-gray-50 font-bold border border-gray-90 dark:border-gray-10">App Store</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-1 md:gap-8">
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-sm font-bold leading-6 text-gray-0 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Connect</h3>
						<ul role="list" class="mt-6 space-y-4">
							<li>
								<a href="https://github.com/Gem-Map" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-50 hover:text-primary-40 dark:text-gray-90 dark:hover:text-secondary-40 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/rss.xml" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-50 hover:text-primary-40 dark:text-gray-90 dark:hover:text-secondary-40 transition-colors">RSS Feed</a>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-16 border-t border-gray-90/30 pt-8 dark:border-gray-10/50">
			<p class="text-xs leading-5 text-gray-50 dark:text-gray-90">&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Gemmap Team. All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
